Class Base

  • java.lang.Object
    • group24.piazzapanic.Base
  • public class Base
extends java.lang.Object
    Core values like screen size, that will need to access, but nothing will need to modify. THIS CLASS *MUST* HAVE NO DEPENDENCIES ON OTHER CLASSES IN THIS PROJECT.
